{"tid":1417452,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]文宣巴絲入","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:04.000Z","uid":56723,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24f8f7ba011fbc8e35badec812d7fb4fa2961299","tid":1417452,"uid":56723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"小弟呢幾個星期每個weekend都有去發夢，老實講我唔係走到最前線，只係幫手挷下野推下鐵。可能因為我廢，連續去咗幾個星期已經覺得好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但再諗下，我地企後面嘅都叫做有時間抖下，最前線手足佢地每分每秒都處於極緊張嘅狀態，個個星期咁樣對峙其實對我地最高戰力嘅一群係好大損耗，而同時間民意同手足之間嘅諗法都俾人分化緊。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，希望各位文宣手足可以幫手煲大<span style=\"color: red;\">黎緊星期五六日嘅機場和理非活動</span>，一黎可以等殺龍巴絲們休息一個星期，二黎可以搞返大政府想冷處理機場罷工呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗機場一事，可以嘅話其實仲有以下事件可以煲大，麻煩各位岀大量文宣同長輩圖:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 黑警使用過期催淚彈，違反國際法</span><br />\n<br />\n［突發！！！］黑警用過期催淚煙，想炸死示威者！推上國際清算！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382020</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[black]<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 黑警無視普通市民同記者安全，係民居同老人院隔離放tg</span>[/black]<br />\n<br />\n[中英文宣] 香港警察向老人院及民居射催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1371763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1371763</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 中聯辦、港共、警黑合作</span><br />\n<br />\n［緊急］點解葉虎單嘢可以不了了之？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382778</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後，每件事都要加返<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求</span></span></span>呢個終極目標上去，唔好俾林奠有藉口話我地搞港獨去左右民意。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山，前線一路衝，文宣一路backup住你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4c1e4b938d8ea0803e923609c78ed1d09e8ce30a","tid":1417452,"uid":56723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"PUsh"},{"pid":"301f505e2dbe4d03ee931eb77f5b665370571d58","tid":1417452,"uid":56723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0681500d57be4ccd31541fc9da1f98c76e201547","tid":1417452,"uid":56723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd6eb50b2098bb0e93d201f5bf78a9f3ddc101f","tid":1417452,"uid":56723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a7eacbcf75028d0fab8406a6fc5b740c29c31f94","tid":1417452,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:21:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"14e3ab9f3d979f80c4b02760b82dbadb2a7aaab6","tid":1417452,"uid":56723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7eacbcf75028d0fab8406a6fc5b740c29c31f94","tid":1417452,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:21:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"終於有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0337e7d54ce5f7779a97fb9520c0670c5b9914a8","tid":1417452,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"4beb8a2c203a95576c0fcf17cf9c7ecee1721b48","tid":1417452,"uid":56723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:37:04.000Z","msg":"食飯推一推"}]}